03:01:52.020 --> 03:01:58.260
on Earth, not slightly more, dramatically, anomalously, inexplicably more.

03:01:59.880 --> 03:02:03.100
The reason lives inside the atom itself.

03:02:03.520 --> 03:02:06.500
Every electron does two things simultaneously.

03:02:06.820 --> 03:02:12.500
It orbits the nucleus like a planet around a star, and it spins on its own axis like a

03:02:12.500 --> 03:02:13.240
tiny top.

03:02:13.980 --> 03:02:17.900
In lighter elements, these two motions barely register each other.

03:02:17.900 --> 03:02:24.220
But bismuth sits near the bottom of the periodic table at element 83, one of the heaviest stable

03:02:24.220 --> 03:02:25.620
elements that exists.

03:02:25.880 --> 03:02:29.760
